<!--

 ============================================
    HEADER: Site branding + top navigation
    The <header> tag represents introductory content
===============================================

============================================
    MAIN: The primary content of the page
    Only ONE <main> per page — this is the rule
=============================================== 
<section> groups related content with a theme
action="#" means "don't navigate away"
The novalidate attribute is a boolean HTML5
<aside> = content tangentially related to main content
<dl> = Description List: pairs of terms and descriptions
-->